author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Mj Gleeson Says HY ‍Unit Sales Increased 31.5 Percent To 593 Units​
text:
Feb 19 (Reuters) - Mj Gleeson Plc:
* HY ‍UNIT SALES INCREASED 31.5% TO 593 UNITS​ * ‍HY REVENUE INCREASED 34.7% TO £73.7M​ * ‍INTERIM DIVIDEND INCREASED 38.5% TO 9.0 PENCE PER SHARE​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
